tafsir[5]{c,v,t}:
  15,32,"Alla daalani Ibuliisa ɓaawo o haɗitaade sujjangol Aadama: E ko haɗu maa sujjidugol e Malaa'ika'en ɓen sujjirɓe ɗoftagol yamiroore Am?"
  15,38,"Haa e ñalaande nde fow maayata nden si allaadu ndun wuttaama araunuru."
  15,40,"Si wanaa ɓen ɓe suɓiɗaa e jeyaaɓe Maa fii ko rewa Maa."
  15,43,"Pellet Jahannama wonii fodoore Ibuliisa e ɓen jokkuɓe mo e majjuɓe ɓen fow."
  15,51,"Humpitaa ɓe kadi fii Malaa'ikaaɓe hoɓɓe Annabi Ibraahiima ɓen addannooɓe mo welo-welo ɓiɗɗo gorko e halkeede yimɓe Luuti ɓen."